<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "profile.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>This journey has always been about being the best father I can be. My experience in other industries fueled my desire to pursue development. I've always had an interest in how things function and being able to create things. Development gives me an avenue to do both. I know that I am just starting my journey as developer, but I am excited to continue to learn and grow as I find my way up this path of dvelopment.</p>

				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-control="jobHistory"
					>
						Job History
					</button>

					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-control="education"
					>
						Education
					</button>
				</p>

				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Compliance Consultant
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Residential Coordinator
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Account Development Manager
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Direct Support Professional
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Security Guard
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Bottega Tech
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Utah Valley Unversity
						</div>
					</div>

				</p>
			</div>
